Class MyCircle

java.lang.Object
MyCircle
public class MyCircle
extends java.lang.Object
Creates a baseline for a circle. The constructor requires no parameters and creates a random radius within the margins defined by the MIN_RADIUS and the MAX_RADIUS. Other useful methods are created to easily calculate the properties of the circle given the randomly generated radius.
Author:
Wil Simpson
